verses.roman:
tabe rāmānanda, āra satyarāja khāṅna
prabhura caraṇe kichu kaila nivedana

synonyms: tabe—after this; rāmānanda—Rāmānanda Vasu; āra—and; satyarāja khāṅna—Satyarāja Khān; prabhura caraṇe—at the lotus feet of Lord Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; kichu—some; kaila—made; nivedana—submission.
translation: After this, Rāmānanda Vasu and Satyarāja Khān both submitted questions at the lotus feet of Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu.
